* [[詹姆斯·法蘭科|詹姆斯·法蘭科]]飾演[[哈里·奥斯本|哈利·奧斯本]]<ref name=“DocOckCast”>{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1470059/spider-man-2-villain-doc-ock-cast/ |title='Spider-Man 2' Villain Doc Ock Cast |last=Downey |first=Ryan J. |publisher=[[MTV|MTV]] |date=2003-02-20 |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817202740/http://www.mtv.com/news/1470059/spider-man-2-villain-doc-ock-cast/ |archive-date=2020-08-17 |url-status=live}}</ref>，彼得的摯友，父親[[诺曼·奥斯本|諾曼·奧斯本]]死後接手{{link-en|奧氏企業|Oscorp}}，贊助奧托的研究。哈利將父親之死怪罪於蜘蛛人，依然想找到蜘蛛人來為父報仇。
: 法蘭科在受訪時表示，為了詮釋出哈利與彼得的真摯友誼，他在幕後與彼得的演員麥奎爾建立起良好的關係：「如果彼得應該成為我（哈利）的長年好友，那麼我認為，去多了解陶比一點應該會有幫助」<ref name="SuperHeroHype.com-Franco">{{cite news|url=https://www.superherohype.com/features/85995-interview-james-franco-talks-spider-man-2|title=INTERVIEW: James Franco Talks Spider-Man 2!|publisher=SuperHeroHype.com|date=2004-06-21|accessdate=2019-11-09|archive-date=2020-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217094223/https://www.superherohype.com/features/85995-interview-james-franco-talks-spider-man-2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

* [[艾佛烈·蒙利納|艾佛烈·蒙利納]]飾演[[八爪博士|奧托·奧克塔維斯 / 八爪博士]]<ref name="EightArmsToHoldYou">{{cite news|first=Brian|last=Hiatt|title=Eight Arms to Hold You|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2003-02-13|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,424644~10~0~spider-man2getsits,00.html|accessdate=2007-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070516112955/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,424644~10~0~spider-man2getsits,00.html|archive-date=2007-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>，知名核物理學家，畢生精力都花在核融合研究上，致力於造福人類的他，因實驗失敗而變成靠四條機械手行動的八爪博士。
: 蒙利納在獲選不久即開始進行體能訓練<ref name="EightArmsToHoldYou" />。導演[[山姆·雷米|山姆·雷米]]對蒙利納在《[[揮灑烈愛|揮灑烈愛]]》（2002年）中的演技感到印象深刻，並認為他的體格很適合擔當此角<ref name="RaimiIGNInterview">{{cite news|first=Jeff|last=Otto|title=Interview: Sam Raimi|publisher=IGN|date=2004-06-29|url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/527/527156p2.html|accessdate=2007-04-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120518000432/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/527/527156p2.html|archivedate=2012-05-18}}</ref>。蒙利納當初在試鏡時僅簡短的討論了這個角色，並沒有察覺自己是個有力的人選<ref name="Amazing">{{cite video|title=Making the Amazing|format=DVD|publisher=Sony|year=2004}}</ref>。身為[[漫威漫畫|漫威漫畫]]迷的蒙利納對於獲選一事興奮不已<ref name="Fan">{{cite news|first=Anwar|last=Brett|title=Alfred Molina|publisher=BBC|date=2004-07-09|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2004/07/09/alfred_molina_spiderman_2_interview.shtml|accessdate=2007-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060228125737/http://www.bbc.co.uk/films/2004/07/09/alfred_molina_spiderman_2_interview.shtml|archive-date=2006-02-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然對八爪博士不甚熟悉，但蒙利納發覺八爪博士的一個特點——不留情且諷刺的[[幽默感|幽默感]]，並想在片中保留這點<ref name="humor">{{cite news|first=Jeff|last=Otto|title=Interview: Tobey Maguire and Alfred Molina|publisher=IGN|date=2004-06-25|url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/526/526417p1.html|accessdate=2007-04-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120518000440/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/526/526417p1.html|archivedate=2012-05-18}}</ref>。在選定蒙利納之前，八爪博士的演員人選還包含[[艾德·哈里斯|艾德·哈里斯]]、[[克里斯·庫柏|克里斯·庫柏]]、[[克里斯托弗·沃肯|克里斯托弗·沃肯]]和[[勞勃·狄尼洛|勞勃·狄尼洛]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tvguide.com/news/alfred-molina-octopus-37245/|title=Meet Spider-Man 2's Dr. Octopus|date=2004-05-20|first=Angel|last=Cohn|website=TV Guide|access-date=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2020-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230091052/https://www.tvguide.com/news/alfred-molina-octopus-37245/ |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tvguide.com/news/alfred-molina-octopus-37245/|title=Meet Spider-Man 2's Dr. Octopus|date=2004-05-20|first=Angel|last=Cohn|website=TV Guide|access-date=2020-12-16 |archive-date=2020-12-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230091052/https://www.tvguide.com/news/alfred-molina-octopus-37245/ |url-status=live|quote="[Director] Sam Raimi saw a whole bunch of us character actors," Molina reveals. "It was me, Ed Harris, Chris Cooper and Christopher Walken. We were all actors on a list because we all had movies that made a bit of a splash.}}</ref>。

