* [[丹尼爾·吉爾斯|丹尼爾·吉爾斯]]飾演{{link-en|約翰·詹姆森 (漫威漫畫)|John Jameson (comics)|約翰·詹姆森}}，J·喬納·詹姆森之子，瑪莉珍的未婚夫<ref name="EWJuly2003" />，是一位[[宇航員|宇航員]]兼國家英雄。

此外，演員[[布魯斯·坎貝爾|布魯斯·坎貝爾]]繼前作後再次客串<ref name="CampbellCameo">{{cite news|first=Patrick|last=Cavanaugh|url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/2018/08/17/bruce-campbell-spider-man-superhero-movies-problem/|title=Bruce Campbell Discusses the Real Problem With Superhero Movies|publisher=Comicbook.com|date=2018-08-17|accessdate=2018-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180818112904/https://comicbook.com/marvel/2018/08/17/bruce-campbell-spider-man-superhero-movies-problem/|archive-date=2018-08-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，飾演的角色為劇院招待員，他因為彼得遲到而拒絕他入場<ref>{{cite web |url=https://screenrant.com/spider-man-movie-trilogy-bruce-campbell-cameos/ |title=Spider-Man: Every Bruce Campbell Cameo in Sam Raimi's Trilogy |last=Behbakht |first=Andy |website=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]] |date=2020-02-20 |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200306165134/https://screenrant.com/spider-man-movie-trilogy-bruce-campbell-cameos/ |archive-date=2020-03-06 |url-status=live}}</ref>。蜘蛛人的創作者之一[[史丹·李|史丹·李]]客串飾演蜘蛛人和八爪博士在銀行大樓上戰鬥時，在下方營救群眾的市民<ref name="LeeCameo">{{cite web|title=From 'X-Men' to 'Spider-Man': 35 of Stan Lee's Most Memorable Cameos|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/stan-lee-cameo-spider-man-homecoming-34-more-films-tv-shows-1018027/item/trial-incredible-hulk-1989-stan-lee-cameos-1989-2017-1018032|accessdate=2018-06-19|date=2017-07-19|last=Berggren|first=Victoria|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621093218/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/stan-lee-cameo-spider-man-homecoming-34-more-films-tv-shows-1018027/item/trial-incredible-hulk-1989-stan-lee-cameos-1989-2017-1018032|archivedate=2018-06-21|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.insider.com/stan-lee-marvel-cameos-2017-3 |title=Stan Lee has made 60 cameos in the Marvel universe — here they all are |last1=Oswald |first1=Anjelica |last2=Acuna |first2=Kirsten |website=[[Insider_(website)|Insider]] |date=2019-04-26 |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20201222230139/https://www.insider.com/stan-lee-marvel-cameos-2017-3 |archive-date=2020-12-22 |url-status=live }}</ref>。[[迪倫·貝克|迪倫·貝克]]飾演彼得的獨臂大學教授[[蜥蜴人|柯特·康納斯]]<ref name="AICN" />，與奧托是朋友關係，也是因為他才讓彼得注意到奧托的研究。演員[[威廉·達佛|威廉·達佛]]回歸出演該片，飾演的角色同樣是[[諾曼·奧斯朋|諾曼·奧斯本]]，哈利已故的父親，僅在哈利的幻覺中現身。達佛在宣傳前作時想出了這個點子，並拿《[[哈姆雷特|哈姆雷特]]》中-{哈}-姆雷特王子見到已逝父王之鬼魂的橋段來做比較<ref name="DafoeCameo">{{cite news|first=Jeff|last=Otto|title=Spidey 2 Talk|publisher=IGN|date=2004-06-25|url=http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/527/527428p1.html|accessdate=2007-04-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120518000453/http://uk.movies.ign.com/articles/527/527428p1.html|archivedate=2012-05-18}}</ref>。

[[伊莉莎白·班克絲|伊莉莎白·班克絲]]回歸飾演貝蒂·布蘭特（{{lang|en|Betty Brant}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/jun/22/elizabeth-banks-i-was-too-old-for-spider-man-girlfriend-role-at-28 |title=Elizabeth Banks: I was 'too old' for Spider-Man girlfriend role at 28 |last=Pulver |first=Andrew |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=2016-06-22 |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225131937/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/jun/22/elizabeth-banks-i-was-too-old-for-spider-man-girlfriend-role-at-28 |archive-date=2020-02-25 |url-status=live}}</ref>，《號角日報》總機，J·喬納·詹姆森的秘書。{{link-en|約翰·帕克斯頓|John Paxton}}回歸飾演奧斯本家保鑣伯納德·豪斯曼（Bernard Houseman）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/red-carpet-flashback-15-years-slideshow-wp-201035545/photo-p-bill-paxton-accompanied-father-photo-201035409.html |title=Red Carpet Flashback! 15 Years of Spider-Man Movies |last=Mucci |first=Gianna |website=[[Yahoo!_Entertainment|Yahoo! Entertainment]] |page=6 |date=2017-07-06 |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222231221/https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/red-carpet-flashback-15-years-slideshow-wp-201035545/photo-p-bill-paxton-accompanied-father-photo-201035409.html |archive-date=2020-12-22 |url-status=live}}</ref>。導演雷米的兄弟{{link-en|泰德·雷米|Ted Raimi}}再度飾演報社頭版編輯霍夫曼（{{lang|en|Hoffman}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://news.avclub.com/r-i-p-do-the-right-thing-and-spider-man-s-bill-nunn-1798252282 |title=R.I.P. ''Do The Right Thing'' and ''Spider-Man''{{'s}} Bill Nunn |last=Hughes |first=William |website=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]] |date=2016-09-24 |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208202929/https://news.avclub.com/r-i-p-do-the-right-thing-and-spider-man-s-bill-nunn-1798252282 |archive-date=2019-12-08 |url-status=live}}</ref>，而{{link-en|比爾·納恩|Bill Nunn}}也回歸飾演《號角日報》編輯{{link-en|羅比·羅伯森 (漫威漫畫)|Robbie Robertson (comics)|羅比·羅伯森}} <ref name="Moviehole" />。{{link-en|埃利亞·貝斯金|Elya Baskin}}飾演彼得的房東迪科維奇先生（{{lang|en|Mr. Ditkovitch}}），而其女兒厄蘇拉（{{lang|en|Ursula}}）則由[[瑪吉娜·托娃|瑪吉娜·托娃]]飾演<ref name="BFI">{{Cite web |url=https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b8a2231b7 |title=Spider-man 2 (2004) |publisher=[[British_Film_Institute|British Film Institute]] |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222121403/https://www2.bfi.org.uk/films-tv-people/4ce2b8a2231b7 |archive-date=2020-12-22 |access-date=2020-12-22}}</ref>。[[克里夫·羅勃遜|克里夫·羅勃遜]]在閃回片段中再度飾演[[班·帕克|班·帕克]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/into-the-spider-verse-features-a-sneaky-cliff-robertson-cameo-as-sam-raimis-uncle-ben |title=Into the Spider-Verse Features a Sneaky Cliff Robertson Cameo as Sam Raimi's Uncle Ben |last=Weiss |first=Josh |website=[[Syfy_Wire|Syfy Wire]] |date=2019-03-11 |access-date=2020-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181229015431/https://www.syfy.com/syfywire/into-the-spider-verse-features-a-sneaky-cliff-robertson-cameo-as-sam-raimis-uncle-ben |archive-date=2018-12-29 |url-status=live}}</ref>。

