2004年3月，索尼開始《蜘蛛人3》的籌拍作業<ref name="Sequel">{{cite news|first=Nicole|last=Laporte|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117901100?refCatId=13|title=Spidey spins web for a third time|publisher=Variety|date=2004-03-02|accessdate=2006-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110805120827/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117901100?refCatId=13|archive-date=2011-08-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由[[山姆·雷米|山姆·雷米]]執導，劇情講述彼得·帕克對抗變成新一代[[綠惡魔|綠惡魔]]的摯友[[哈里·奥斯本|哈利·奧斯本]]，以及兩名新反派[[沙人_(漫威漫畫)|沙人]]（[[托马斯·哈登·丘奇|托馬斯·哈登·丘奇]]飾演）與[[猛毒|猛毒]]（[[陶佛·葛瑞斯|陶佛·葛瑞斯]]飾演）的故事<ref name="Sequel2">{{cite news|first=Heather|last=Newgen|title=Spider-Man 3 Interviews: Director Sam Raimi|publisher=Superherohype.com|date=2007-04-21|url=http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/93443-spider-man-3-interviews-director-sam-raimi|accessdate=2007-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121021123842/http://www.superherohype.com/features/articles/93443-spider-man-3-interviews-director-sam-raimi|archive-date=2012-10-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Sequel3">{{cite news|author=Richard George|url=http://comics.ign.com/articles/720/720542p1.html|title=Comic-Con 2006: Spider-Man 3|publisher=IGN|date=2006-07-23|accessdate=2006-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120723031207/http://comics.ign.com/articles/720/720542p1.html|archive-date=2012-07-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Sequel4">{{cite news|author=Larry Carroll|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1537122/07252006/story.jhtml|title='Spider-Man 3' Cast Confirms Love Triangle, Death, Soul-Sucking Costume|publisher=MTV|date=2006-07-26|accessdate=2006-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070102104706/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1537122/07252006/story.jhtml|archive-date=2007-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《蜘蛛人3》於2005年11月開拍，2006年7月[[殺青|殺青]]，並於2007年5月4日在北美上映<ref name="Sequel5">{{cite news|author=Grant Curtis|url=http://www.sonypictures.com/movies/spiderman3/blog/archives/2006/07/welcome_back.php|title=Grant Curtis – Welcome back|publisher=Spider-Man 3 Movie Blog|date=2006-07-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012191639/http://sonypictures.com/movies/spiderman3/blog/archives/2006/07/welcome_back.php|archivedate=2007-10-12|accessdate=2006-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Sequel6">{{cite news|first=Ian|last=Mohr|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117964093?refCatId=13|title='Spider-Man 3' sets records|publisher=Variety|date=2007-05-01|accessdate=2007-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121106155841/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117964093?refCatId=13|archive-date=2012-11-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 演員回歸漫威电影宇宙 ===
經過多年以後，[[漫威工作室|漫威工作室]]開啟了新的蜘蛛人電影系列。2020年12月8日，[[Collider|Collider]]披露，舊系列的演員將會透過多元宇宙的設定再度回歸，本系列的蜘蛛人演員[[陶比·麥奎爾|陶比·麥奎爾]]正在為回歸事宜進行討論，而女主角[[克斯汀·鄧斯特|克莉絲汀·鄧斯特]]和《[[蜘蛛侠系列电影#马克·韦布系列（Earth-120703）|驚奇再起系列]]》的蜘蛛人演員[[安德魯·加菲爾德|安德魯·加菲爾德]]已經確定回歸<ref name="MolinaDunstGarfieldSM3">{{Cite web |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |date=2020-12-08 |title=New 'Spider-Man' Movie Bringing Back Doctor Octopus and Past Peter Parkers |url=https://collider.com/spider-man-3-cast-doc-ock-alfred-molina-andrew-garfield/ |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208203641/https://collider.com/spider-man-3-cast-doc-ock-alfred-molina-andrew-garfield/ |archive-date=2020-12-08 |access-date=2020-12-08 |website=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]] }}</ref>。本片的演員[[艾佛烈·蒙利納|艾佛烈·蒙利納]]也將回歸出演[[八爪博士|奧托·奧克塔維斯／八爪博士]]<ref name="Molina">{{Cite web |last=Kit |first=Borys |last2=Couch |first2=Aaron |date=2020-12-08 |title='Spider-Man 3': Alfred Molina Returning as Doctor Octopus |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/spider-man-3-alfred-molina-returning-as-doctor-octopus |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208184542/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/spider-man-3-alfred-molina-returning-as-doctor-octopus |archive-date=2020-12-08 |access-date=2020-12-08 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] }}</ref>。2021年2月，麥奎爾和加菲爾德回歸的傳聞被[[湯姆·荷蘭|湯姆·荷蘭]]否認<ref name="HollandFeb2021Fallon">{{Cite web |last=Beresford |first=Trilby |date=2021-02-23 |title=Tom Holland Is Tight Lipped on Tobey Maguire, Andrew Garfield Cameos in 'Spider-Man': "It Would Be a Miracle If They Kept That From Me" |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tom-holland-is-tight-lipped-on-tobey-maguire-andrew-garfield-cameos-in-spider-man-it-would-be-a-miracle-if-they-kept-that-from-me |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224134901/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/tom-holland-is-tight-lipped-on-tobey-maguire-andrew-garfield-cameos-in-spider-man-it-would-be-a-miracle-if-they-kept-that-from-me |archive-date=2021-02-24 |access-date=2021-02-24 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]}}</ref><ref name="HollandFeb2021GQ">{{Cite web |last=Heaf |first=Jonathan |date=2021-02-26 |title=Tom Holland on his darkest role yet, and why No Way Home could be his last Spider-Man film |url=https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/culture/article/tom-holland-cherry-interview |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227035541/https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/culture/article/tom-holland-cherry-interview |archive-date=2021-02-26 |access-date=2021-02-26 |website={{link-en|英國GQ|British GQ|British GQ}}}}</ref>。蒙利納在2021年4月證實出演消息<ref name="MolinaDetails">{{Cite web |last=Aurthur |first=Kate |date=2021-04-16 |title=Alfred Molina Details Doc Ock's Return in 'Spider-Man: No Way Home': 'The Tentacles Do All the Work' (Exclusive) |url=https://variety.com/2021/film/news/alfred-molina-spider-man-no-way-home-doc-ock-1234953527/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416232314/https://variety.com/2021/film/news/alfred-molina-spider-man-no-way-home-doc-ock-1234953527/ |archive-date=2021-04-16 |access-date=2021-04-16 |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]}}</ref>，並已在8月釋出的預告片亮相<ref name="EWTrailer">{{Cite web |last=Coggan |first=Devan |date=2021-08-23 |title=Spider-Man: No Way Home trailer reintroduces some familiar faces |url=https://ew.com/movies/spider-man-no-way-home-trailer/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210824032930/https://ew.com/movies/spider-man-no-way-home-trailer/ |archive-date=2021-08-24 |access-date=2021-08-23 |website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]}}</ref>。《[[蜘蛛人：無家日|蜘蛛人：無家日]]》於2021年12月17日上映<ref name="December2021Date">{{Cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/spider-man-far-from-home-sequel-delayed-1234715451/ |title=‘Spider-Man: Far From Home’ Sequel Delayed to December 2021 |last=Moreau |first=Jordan |date=2020-07-23 |website=[[Variety_(m